text: Alton is an unincorporated community in St. Tammany Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located north of Slidell on U.S. Route 11 1.25 miles north of I-12.Slidell, LA, 7.5 Minute Topographic Quadrangle, USGS, 1971 (1994 rev.) ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in St. Tammany Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in New Orleans metropolitan area
